lead_paragraph: Spieth, who is five shots back at the Deutsche Bank Championship after a 68, has already qualified for the season-ending Tour Championship.

headline.print_headline: Spieth Is Chasing a FedEx Cup First: A Repeat Title
headline.main: Jordan Spieth Is Chasing a FedEx Cup First: A Repeat Title

snippet: Spieth, who is five shots back at the Deutsche Bank Championship after a 68, has already qualified for the season-ending Tour Championship....
abstract: Jordan Spieth is in strong position to win FedEx Cup for second year in row as he finishes strongly in Deutsche Bank Championship; no player has been champion for two consecutive years since cup began in 2007.
